    "synopsis": "For months the Necron World Engine — a vast, mobile construct the size of a planet — has carved a path of ruin through the Vidar sector, shattering worlds and destroying every fleet sent against it. With billions of lives in the balance, the Astral Knights stake everything on a single desperate plan: crash their battle-barge onto the construct's surface and fight their way to its heart. Led by Chapter Master Artor Amhrad, the Astral Knights land amid tens of thousands of Necrons and wage a relentless war through forge and weapon-node, paying for every yard in blood. It is a battle that will define a Chapter — and demand the ultimate price.",
